.Dd January 29, 2004
.Dt SUNLABEL 8
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm sunlabel
.Nd read and write disk pack label suitable for Sun's OpenBoot PROM
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Op Fl r
.Ar disk
.Nm
.Fl B
.Op Fl b Ar boot1
.Op Fl n
.Ar disk
.Nm
.Fl R
.Op Fl B Op Fl b Ar boot1
.Op Fl r
.Op Fl n
.Ar disk profile
.Nm
.Fl e
.Op Fl B Op Fl b Ar boot1
.Op Fl r
.Op Fl n
.Ar disk
.Nm
.Fl w
.Op Fl B Op Fl b Ar boot1
.Op Fl r
.Op Fl n
.Ar disk type
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
utility
installs, examines or modifies the bootable
.Fx
label on a disk partition.
In addition,
.Nm
can install bootstrap code.
.Sh FILES
.Bl -tag -width ".Pa /boot/boot1" -compact
.It Pa /boot/boot1
Default boot image.
.El
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr geom 4 ,
.Xr disktab 5 ,
.Xr bsdlabel 8
